title: Contact
text: This website gives an overview over all publicly available software packages created by members of MSS. This website is created and managed by Methods for Model-based Development in Computational Engineering (MBD) under the supervision of Uni.-Prof. Dr. sc. habil. Julia Kowalski. So far only software of MBD is featured have been incorporated.
